Layout Structure:
- Top: Two-column text (595px + 583px) with Menu button on right
- Middle: Full-width image carousel
- Bottom: Footer with Colophon/Thank You + Social links

Grid Breakdown:
- Top section: 12 columns
- Colophon section: 6 columns each
- Social links: Right-aligned

Accessibility:
- Section: role="contentinfo" or "region" with aria-label="About"
- Social links: List with proper link text (not just icons)
